snippet.title: Divide By Sheep Story Trailer - July 2nd
snippet.description:
Divide By Sheep is a game about friendship and slicing sheep in half. A very not-so-typical math puzzler. 

http://DivideBySheep.com 

Coming to Steam and iOS
